body_html: I got a similar issue when trying to build pytorch for Mac OS high sierra 10.13.6. Interestingly the issue happened only when building in python3. When I built it with python2.7 the problem didn't come up. As mentioned before the building of the code is OK, the problem occurs when linking. I did pull the latest version and tried again and it worked the last time. My problem might have been that I had to start with a clean and updated code
